<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_e88c525a-8a90-4c6a-85fa-c62a9686c68e" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>13.7.9</sptc><title id="_becb1584-dcf1-40c8-9c2f-d4ac73b1d0b6">Spa pool heating and pumping</title><archive-num>2019: 3.12.5.8</archive-num><subclause id="_9cd8c14b-6eff-4672-a3b0-34f74ea910de" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_fc684212-c463-469c-83b4-829381954a80">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Heating for a spa pool that shares a water recirculation system with a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_8286b337-f0da-485e-85ed-9ed0804b972c" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must be by—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_bcc8d7b9-d2ca-45a3-90ae-a1107f21db47">a solar heater; or</li><li id="_ed396142-2709-4d18-8f0f-d733cea46ef1">a heater using reclaimed energy; or</li><li id="_f51f8670-38cf-4816-ac76-65dd8d7d4b67">a gas heater; or</li><li id="_87c52e9b-04c4-4097-a2c4-199c692f4a28">a heat pump; or</li><li id="_92d75ac4-2493-4b0d-a413-5de436703df6">a combination of (a) to (d).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_aab6e740-35d3-4547-8ab3-96e03a0a5f57" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_63c0ec01-e576-4630-8c71-7ef45b18b71b">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Where some or all of the heating <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_6d5e4a70-c4b7-468b-982c-075b998ff73a" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (1) is by a gas heater or a heat pump, the spa pool must have—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_c15feb72-98ce-4ef6-8588-f0ff9e6f5b72">a cover; and</li><li id="_732df627-6b68-44fd-bf76-33997e43987c">a push button and a time switch to control the operation of the heater.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_5cfd2d37-16b0-458a-8036-dabf665f2124" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_02bedc62-6646-4cf4-8e6f-5797461c8c12">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A time switch must be provided to control the operation of a circulation pump for a spa pool having a capacity of 680 L or more.</p></subclause></clause>